actual transactions.

00:28:03.250 --> 00:28:07.570
When the code is redeemed in
Play Store, outside of game,

00:28:07.570 --> 00:28:09.950
the thing will be a
little bit different.

00:28:09.950 --> 00:28:11.875
You can redeem the
code before installing,

00:28:11.875 --> 00:28:14.050
or while running the app.

00:28:14.050 --> 00:28:16.840
In that case, you
can handle redemption

00:28:16.840 --> 00:28:19.390
when the game starts.

00:28:19.390 --> 00:28:21.470
When the code is
redeemed in Play Store

00:28:21.470 --> 00:28:24.180
while your game
is up and running,

00:28:24.180 --> 00:28:26.310
the store will
let your game know

00:28:26.310 --> 00:28:29.760
that there is an update by
sending an intent called

00:28:29.760 --> 00:28:32.560
PurchasesUpdate.

00:28:32.560 --> 00:28:36.820
So your game should listen
to this intent and handle it.

00:28:36.820 --> 00:28:41.820
Please note that there will be
no orderId or developer payload

00:28:41.820 --> 00:28:44.670
when redeemed in Play Store.

00:28:44.670 --> 00:28:48.320
Let's quickly look at the
code snippets of the last case

00:28:48.320 --> 00:28:51.040
I just mentioned.

00:28:51.040 --> 00:28:54.880
You should register a broadcast
receiver for the intent

00:28:54.880 --> 00:28:56.790
when your activities
are resumed,

00:28:56.790 --> 00:29:00.880
and unregister it
when it's paused.

00:29:00.880 --> 00:29:03.660
On the same method
of the receiver,

00:29:03.660 --> 00:29:09.020
you can handle the
purchased item as user,

00:29:09.020 --> 00:29:13.690
but you will see neither a
orderId nor developer payload,

00:29:13.690 --> 00:29:16.700
since it was not real,
actual transaction,

00:29:16.700 --> 00:29:21.150
and purchase didn't
happen within game.

00:29:21.150 --> 00:29:26.020
In many cases, I recommend to
create a separate in-app item

00:29:26.020 --> 00:29:30.660
which is not visible inside the
game just for promo code only.

00:29:30.660 --> 00:29:34.870
It's way easier to sort out
the purchase-by-redemption

00:29:34.870 --> 00:29:38.430
from those by actual payment.

